06 000 so'm). Amal qilish muddati — 10 yil."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Pasport yo'qotilganda qancha turadi?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Ikki baravar boj. Xorijga chiqish pasporti: odatdagi 2 BHK o'rniga 4 BHK (1 648 000 so'm)."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Pasportni qayerda rasmiylashtirish mumkin?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"my.gov.uz orqali onlayn yoki propiska joyi bo'yicha IIBda shaxsan. To'lov Click, Payme, Uzum yoki bank orqali."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Xorijga chiqish pasporti uchun qanday hujjatlar kerak?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Ariza, amaldagi pasport yoki tug'ilganlik guvohnomasi, 35×45 mm foto, boj to'lovi kvitansiyasi."}}]},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"TechArticle","headline":"Pasport yig'imlari","description":"O'zbekiston pasporti uchun davlat boji miqdorini hisoblang. Biometrik, xorijga chiqish pasporti va almashtirish.","url":"https://calk.uz/uz/calculator/pasport-yigimlari","datePublished":"2025-08-02","dateModified":"2025-10-05","author":{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://calk.uz/#founder","name":"Konstantin Yakovlev","alternateName":"Константин Яковлев","url":"https://calk.uz/uz/author/konstantin-yakovlev","jobTitle":"Calk.UZ loyihasi asoschisi va rahbari","image":"https://calk.uz/og/author-konstantin.jpg"},"reviewedBy":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Calk.UZ","url":"https://calk.uz"},"publisher":{"@type":"Organization","@id":"https://calk.uz/#organization","name":"Calk.UZ","url":"https://calk.uz","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://calk.uz/favicon.svg"}},"inLanguage":"uz","mainEntityOfPage":"https://calk.uz/uz/calculator/pasport-yigimlari"},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"HowTo","name":"Pasport yig'imlaridan qanday foydalanish","description":"Pasport yig'imlaridan foydalanish bo'yicha qadam-baqadam qo'llanma","totalTime":"PT1M","step":[{"@type":"HowToStep","position":1,"name":"Pasport turini tanlang","text":"Turni ko'rsating: biometrik, xizmat, diplomatik.